name: marine electric motor construction | marine electric motor | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/18600/documentation

This dataset represents the construction of electric motors and pumps used in marine applications, per 1000 kg of motor, based on an average electric motor composition.

Provision of materials, construction of marine electric motors and pumps.

Metal works as proxy for the construction and assembly of all motor parts. End of life treatment. The Use phase of motors is modelled in the vessel's Use phase.
category: A:Agriculture, forestry and fishing/03:Fishing and aquaculture/031:Fishing/0311:Marine fishing

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: Data based on literature on marine electric motor and pump composition, as well as data from marine engine providers, contractors for vessel maintenance and refurbishing work, shipyard operators. Primary data on motors weight from 143 vessels
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Peru features various shipyards and relevant ship-building and ship-retrofitting expertise.
